summary: SummaryHighlightsClean IngredientsVeganThe KYLIE COSMETICS Matte Lip Kit lets you create Kylie's long-lasting matte lip looks. This Matte Liquid Lipstick & Lip Liner duo is the perfect ready-to-go lip routine. The highly pigmented formulas are vegan.
details: DetailsBenefitsThe KYLIE COSMETICS Matte Lip Kit is an all-in-one pair featuring one full-size Matte Liquid Lipstick and one full-size Pencil Lip LinerShape with the Lip Pencil, fill in with the Matte Liquid LipstickLip Liner: Ultra-creamy, waterproof, transfer-proof, smudge-proofLong-lasting 24-hour wearIdeally pairs with all lip textures: Matte, Velvet, GlossMatte Liquid Lipstick: True-matte non-sticky finishLong-lasting 8-hour wearInstant-setting color payoffResearch Results98% agreed the product brings more definition and sculpt the lips100% agreed the product prevents lipstick from smudgingConsumer acceptance test conducted with 50 women between 18-40 years, current users of matte lipstick and lip linerProduct use for 1 weekItem 2583993How To UseFor the best result, line and fill in your lips with the lip liner then top one coat of Matte Liquid Lipstick.IngredientsIsododecane, Mica, Octyldodecanol, Hydrogenated Styrene/Isoprene Copolymer, Stearalkonium Hectorite, Alcohol, Flavor (Aroma), Water (Aqua), Dicalcium Phosphate, Pentaerythrityl Tetra-Di-T-Butyl Hydroxyhydrocinnamate, Tin Oxide, Red 7 Lake (CI 15850), Iron Oxides (CI 77491, CI 77492, CI 77499), Blue 1 Lake (CI 42090), Titanium Dioxide (CI 77891), Yellow 5 Lake (CI 19140).Dimethicone, Trimethylsiloxysilicate, Synthetic Wax, Phenylpropyldimethylsiloxysilicate, Polyethylene, Dicalcium Phosphate, Acrylates/Stearyl Acrylate/Dimethicone Methacrylate Copolymer, Mica, Polyhydroxystearic Acid, Caprylyl Methicone, Disteardimonium Hectorite, Caprylic/Capric Triglyceride, Pentaerythrityl Tetra-Di-T-Butyl Hydroxyhydrocinnamate, Propylene Carbonate, Tocopherol, Rubus Idaeus (Raspberry) Leaf Extract, [+/- : Titanium Dioxide (CI 77891), Iron Oxides (CI 77491, CI 77492), Red 7 Lake (CI 15850), Red 28 Lake (CI 45410), Blue 1 Lake (CI 42090), Yellow 5 Lake (CI 19140)]Shipping & Coupon RestrictionsThis brand is excluded from most Ulta Beauty coupons.See brand eligibility details
how_to_use: For the best result, line and fill in your lips with the lip liner then top one coat of Matte Liquid Lipstick.

reviews.headline: Short term stay
reviews.comments:
Beautiful color.
I can't even get three hours out of this color.  However, if I wanted color only on the very edges of my lips, it would probably be 24hrs, but I really would like color to cover my lips.  This is not long lasting.

reviews.headline: Overpriced doesn't last
reviews.comments: Was very disappointed in this product! Did not last on my lips more than an hour and was overpriced.

reviews.headline: Colors were off
reviews.comments: Colors were not what I was expecting from packaging. It also did not last as long as I expected. I would not purchase again.

reviews.headline: Very drying
reviews.comments: I'm returning this product as I feel it is very drying and pulling on my lips.

reviews.headline: I would buy this product again!
reviews.comments: Long lasting wear, only had to retouch once. Buttery smooth application from lip liner.

reviews.headline: I will never purchase from Ulta Online again
reviews.comments: If I could give zero stars, I would. I have no review on this product because I have yet to receive it nor the replacement one. My order was placed and paid for on July 19th. It's now August 3rd. You're better off going in store than purchasing online

reviews.comments: Love the lipstick. Lip liner is terrible.

reviews.headline: First time buying expensive
reviews.comments: For my first time spending extra money on lip make up, I was so impressed. I had never really used lip liner before, but it changed the while experience for me! The lipstick is high quality and being able to shape your lip makes it all look so much better

reviews.headline: Do not recommend
reviews.comments: This did not stay on at all. The liner is alot smoother than the old version which is nice, but I still would not recommend due to the staying power and that it smears off my lips. The Mary J color is beautiful. The Candy K and Kylie are not flattering at all.

reviews.headline: Love the new formula
reviews.comments: I disliked the old formula and I'm so happy Kylie upgraded it because she has the best colors out there. The new formula is soft and easy to apply. After 4 hours you will need to reapply if you drink or eat but its fine. Still lasts longer than most brands. Love it!

reviews.comments: Love this shade! Received this shade in a promo and fell in love ever since.

reviews.headline: Love it!

reviews.headline: This color matches my lips perfectly
reviews.comments: So it's made it very easy to make my lips look naturally larger

reviews.headline: I will buy again

reviews.headline: Save your money
reviews.comments: The lipstick was incredibly drying and the lip liner lasted a good 2 minutes. Felt incredibly cheap. Save your coins and get you a NYX lip liner and gloss because this is a big NO.

reviews.headline: Worst ever
reviews.comments: Crumbs up on the lips, this after showing you just how many wrinkles you have, and why you shouldn't have gone matte, let alone liquid non-moving lipstick. That is hard to remove but MUST  be removed when it's not doing right by you. Smell is horrendous. I saw this on sale in vending machines at the airport. That should give you a hint to stay off this.

faceoff_positive.comments: i bought this a couple of months ago and still going strong! just completes my makeup i wear it for everyday day makeup or full makeup.. so many questions on where it's from.. stays on for hours no need to worry about it coming off.. would never buy lol products anywhere else
faceoff_positive.headline: AMAZING

faceoff_negative.comments: I was ordering a mini lip kit and a regular lip kit in the same color. When they arrived I had two different colors. When I reached out to the customer service they basically said there was nothing they could do because all sales are final and no exchanges. However it wasn't the color I even ordered! I'm super disappointed with the company and making things right with the customer. The color they sent me would never go with my light complexed skin tone so I will never be able to use it. So that was money down the drain.
faceoff_negative.headline: Terrible costumer service!
